author: AF
title: AF
text:
Tasked with selling a property, I researched agents in the area and chose Tom Alexiadis of Nelson Alexander Northcote over other agents because of his obvious knowledge and experience.
Tom and his team were supportive and empathetic throughout the process and by trusting his recommendations the auction achieved a sales result that exceeded our expectations.
I would not hesitate to recommend Tom and the team at Nelson Alexander Northcote to handle the successful sale of a property.
